latestPosts.caption:
Hey guys! 

I am Abhishek Redwal 🩵

"Khazaana" is a song I poured my heart into, especially because it helped me get over a really tough breakup. It will be available on all streaming platforms on 05/05 🗓️

The song is all about that phase after a breakup when you feel like you've lost something super precious. But as it goes on, it's about realizing that maybe losing that person was actually a good thing. It's a reminder that even when someone leaves, you're still valuable on your own. You're the real treasure. You're the Khazaana 💎

It took us nearly a year to pull the song off and it would never be possible without an extremely amazing set of skilled people, I'm blessed to have them by my side.
